        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "BUG: Strip strikethrough text from context files before sending to model",
        "body": "Addresses #47668\n\nStruck-through text in context files was still being forwarded to the model as-is. This PR fixes that by stripping all strikethrough content in `sanitizeContextFileContentForPrompt()` before the context is embedded in the system prompt. It handles both markdown (`~~text~~`) and HTML variants (`<s>`, `<del>`, `<strike>`), including multiline blocks. The content itself is removed entirely, not just the markers.\n\nChanges are in `src/agents/system-prompt.ts` and `src/agents/system-prompt.test.ts`. Tests added for both inline and multiline cases.",
